2 different pets are kept: bird, lizard
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, van
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the owner of the bird##1
2. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |
| Game    | backgammon       | snooker    |
| Hobby       | skydiving | drawing |
| Pet         | bird      | lizard  |
| Transport   | van       | roller  |

